description: This is an in-progress iOS app for a popular Indian singing game called Antakshari.  The game consists of a certain number of teams, who take turns singing songs that either start with the same letter the previous song ended with, or that fall within certain categories.  This app facilitates playing that game, by providing built-in categories and hints, lyrics search, and easy to manage team, player, and score keeping functionalities.
